summary:
This is my first created house on skyrim creation kit

this house is located between morthal solitude and markarth area
descriptionHtml:
the house includes

bedroom
bookshelfs
mannequins weapon racks
alchemy area
enchantment area

its a nice compact size nothing to big


there is a house for the merchant that lives across from you he is a kjahit called kat
he sells blacksmith items but you can sell most things to hinm and he has plenty of gold

==========================
the key is located on the workbench at the smithing area at the house i was going to put it in the kat\'s merchandise but wouldnt show up so your are now getting it for free :)
==========================
